title: Follow-up on the claim #Qmbkppo
body:
The member has initiated a claim for drastic devaluation of the Shiba Inu coin.
Shiba Inu is a Meme coin/token which is not covered by inSure Defi Community.
This information can be verified on CMC and Coingecko:

https://coinmarketcap.com/currencies/shiba-inu/
https://www.coingecko.com/en/coins/shiba-inu
The minimum eligibility requirements for the coin/token can be found here: https://insuretoken.net/whitepaper.html#faq

[Resolution] The insurance claim cannot be approved, since Shiba Inu is a Meme token.
